name: tb-enumerate
author: Thierry Bazzanella

sections.description:
This plugin allows you to discover the numbering system by position invented by the Hindus, that every day is used unconsciously most of the time. The base recognized by this plugin are from 2 to 26. You can integrate this plugin in your wordpress page with the shortcode [tbenumerate]This plugin allows you to discover the numbering system by position invented by the Hindus, that every day is used unconsciously most of the time.
